Rangabati Song Lyrics from Coke Studio MTV Season 4 with music composed by Ram Sampath. This track is Odisha’s most popular folk song from the Sambalpur region and is widely known since it aired on All India Radio for first time in mid-1970s. Singer Sona Mohapatra sings this beautiful song in Kosli as an ode to her home state Odisha mixed with Tamil Rap by Rajesh and Tony. And talented Rituraj Mohanty adds a patriotic touch to this sensational song with Bande utkala janani verse. The original song is sung by Jitendra Haripal and Krishna Patel with lyrics of rangabati song by Mitrabhanu Guintia and music by Prabhudatta Pradhan. Coke Studio celebrates the voices of many great singers like Arijit Singh, Atif Aslam, and Ankit Tiwari.

Song Credits:
Song: Rangabati
Singer: Rajesh Radhakrishnan, Rituraj Mohanty, Sona Mohapatra, Tony Sebastian
Lyrics: Mitrabhanu Guintia
Music: Ram Sampath

snippet.textDisplay:
This is one amazing work. I heard this for the first few times on Utkal Divas 2021, and with no knowledge of Odia, I could understand a little because I knew words "Bande Utkala Janani" because I could pick up Bande from "Vande" Mataram, Utkala from  "Dravida "Utkala" Banga" of our National Anthem and the Utkal Desha. Janani is synonym for Mother and I studied in my school.

I did a little research, and now I can sing 60-70% of the song without seeing lyrics.

Bande Utkala Janani. Jai Karnataka. Jai Telangana. Jai Andhra Pradesh. And yes- Jai Hind.
snippet.textOriginal:
This is one amazing work. I heard this for the first few times on Utkal Divas 2021, and with no knowledge of Odia, I could understand a little because I knew words "Bande Utkala Janani" because I could pick up Bande from "Vande" Mataram, Utkala from  "Dravida "Utkala" Banga" of our National Anthem and the Utkal Desha. Janani is synonym for Mother and I studied in my school.

I did a little research, and now I can sing 60-70% of the song without seeing lyrics.

Bande Utkala Janani. Jai Karnataka. Jai Telangana. Jai Andhra Pradesh. And yes- Jai Hind.
